        "## Phase 6 - Two Operational Policies\n",
        "\n",
        "We compare three policies via simulation (30 replications each):\n",
        "\n",
        "- **Baseline** - no intervention\n",
        "- **NAR (Network-Aware Reassignment)** - for any slot with predicted p(no-show) > 0.30, pre-stage a same-network, same-specialty standby patient to fill it. Targets the **max-throughput** corner of the policy space.\n",
        "- **RBS (Risk-Buffered Scheduling)** - for any high-risk slot, leave the next slot at that provider empty (30-min buffer). Targets the **min-wait** corner.\n",
        "\n",
        "We measure throughput, wait time, MD utilization, and nurse overtime hours per day.\n"
      ]
    },
